high_descs: Turn around and walk to the bathroom sink.
Take the soap to the bathroom sink.
Put the soapbar in the sink and put on the water.
Take the soap and walk to the living room shelf.
Put the soapbar on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Get the SoapBar to the Shelf in the living room.

high_descs: Leave the room by turning around and head towards the bathroom by crossing the living room and passing the sink.
Pick the soapbar from the side of the sink.
Then move in front of the sink and place the soap inside the sink.
Wet the soapbar by opening the tap water, then close it.
Turn left and head to the shelf in the living room.
Then place the soapbar on the shelf of the cupboard.
anns.task_desc: Place the SoapBar on the Shelf of the cupboard by watering it in the sink.

high_descs: Head rotate and turn left and turn left to the sink.
Pick the soap bar from the sink.
Place the soap bar inside the sink.
Rinse it off, and turn right and turn right to the shelf.
Place the soap bar on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: To place the soap bar on the shelf.
